9b0f6c38e382585f3908988662505030a2434f281c162acd989b916318f0ada8df267a72d62441213c391bf30f9f14a370ce35ec2ba16dae414ccaf45365ff2a  0001-amber-mpris-Add-support-for-building-against-Qt6.patch
"
